    <item>
      <title>亿滋国际考虑收购美国巧克力制造商好时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/mondelez-said-to-explore-takeover-of-us-chocolate-maker-hershey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，零食和糖果公司亿滋国际 (Mondelez International Inc.) 正在探索收购美国标志性巧克力制造商好时公司 (Hershey Co.)，这笔交易可能打造出一家总销售额近 500 亿美元的食品巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/mondelez-said-to-explore-takeover-of-us-chocolate-maker-hershey</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
